Title: The Bone Yard
Plot: NCIS discovers that an area in the Marine's bombing range is where mafia has been dumping the bodies for a while. One of the victims is an undercover FBI agent. The team sets out to find a mole.
GuestStars: John Rosenfeld, Robert Costanzo, Chris Ellis, Brian Dietzen, Mary Pat Gleason, Joe Tabb, Blue Deckert, Joe Spano
